    <section class="feature_part single_feature_padding">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-xl-3 align-self-center">
                    <div class="single_feature_text ">
                        <h2>Novel <br> Features</h2>
                        <p>Get personal attention from teachers and don't let hesitation inhibit your learning. </p>
                        <a href="#about-us" class="btn_1">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-xl-3">
                    <div class="single_feature">
                        <div class="single_feature_part">
                            <span class="single_feature_icon"><i class="ti-layers"></i></span>
                            <h4>Interactive Classes</h4>
                            <p>Get the feel of a real Classroom and tackle the subject at your own pace
                                with regular assessments to ensure a thorough understanding of the subject.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-xl-3">
                    <div class="single_feature">
                        <div class="single_feature_part">
                            <span class="single_feature_icon"><i class="ti-new-window"></i></span>
                            <h4>Expert Trainers</h4>
                            <p>Interact and Learn from IIT/IIM graduates, subject and industry experts,
                                who will be enhanching your understanding of the subject.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-xl-3">
                    <div class="single_feature">
                        <div class="single_feature_part single_feature_part_2">
                            <span class="single_service_icon style_icon"><i class="ti-light-bulb"></i></span>
                            <h4>Job Oppurtunity</h4>
                            <p>Get internship and job opportunities with our partner companies and refferals
                                for MnCs like Microsoft, Amazon,and Jaguar Land Rover.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section id="about-us" class="learning_part">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-sm-center align-items-lg-stretch">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-7">
                    <div class="learning_img">
                        <img src="/img/learning_img.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-5">
                    <div class="learning_member_text">
                        <h5>About us</h5>
                        <h2>Learning with Love
                            and Laughter</h2>
                        <p>Splitzlearn is an ed-tech community run by IIT(ISM) Dhanbad Alumnus, who identified the need
                            of an interactive learner friendly live training for people.
                            It is known that learners are not much comfortable, learning and asking doubts in a large
                            group specially with many unknown mates around.
                            We allow learners to make their own classroom, choose an instructor of their choice and
                            learn in their comfort pace, without paying exorbitant prices.
                            At Splitzlearn we believe that a happy mind is the key for comprehensive learning.
                            A classroom of well connected students, led by an experienced teacher triggers your
                            the overall development.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><span class="ti-pencil-alt"></span>Easy and better grasping of subjects.</li>
                            <li><span class="ti-video-camera"></span>Easily access the recorded classes for your future
                                reference and outshine in tests and interviews.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="member_counter">
